Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.10,0:00:26.72,Default,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Brother, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.38,0:00:29.59,Default,BYAKUYA,0000,0000,0000,,We’re returning to the Soul Society.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.59,0:00:30.46,Default,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.46,0:00:33.22,Default,BYAKUYA,0000,0000,0000,,Have you forgotten, Rukia?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.18,0:00:39.30,Default,BYAKUYA,0000,0000,0000,,We came to see the choice \NIchigo Kurosaki makes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.76,0:00:42.75,Default,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,The Soul Society was aware
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.75,0:00:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that once the next Substitute \NSoul Reaper appeared,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.01,0:00:50.73,Default,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,Ginjo would set his sights \Non him sooner or later.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.37,0:00:52.82,Default,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,When that happened,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.82,0:00:57.61,Default,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,we would use that Substitute \Nto find Ginjo and
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.61,0:01:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,before eliminating them \Nat an appropriate time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.15,0:01:04.16,Default,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,The majority of captains \Nshared that view.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.75,0:01:09.81,Default,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,But our contact with that Substitute \Nchanged the Soul Society.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.47,0:01:12.82,Default,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,We shared our powers with the Substitute
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.82,0:01:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we were supposed to kill
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.55,0:01:17.60,Default,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,and dispatched captains \Nto watch his actions
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.60,0:01:19.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,rather than kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.29,0:01:21.51,Default,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,Kuchiki.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.51,0:01:24.76,Default,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,Remember when you objected to the orders
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.76,0:01:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of keeping watch on Ichigo Kurosaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.66,0:01:30.36,Default,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,That can’t be!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.97,0:01:32.70,Default,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo wouldn’t…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.70,0:01:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He would never succumb to the \Ntemptations of the enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.81,0:01:37.53,Default,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,You were right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.48,0:01:41.84,Default,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo Kurosaki learned the \Ntruth and made his choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.86,0:01:47.15,Default,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,That choice was the very same choice
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.15,0:01:51.29,Default,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,that the Ichigo Kurosaki we knew—
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.29,0:01:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Ichigo Kurosaki you \Nbelieved in—made.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.52,0:02:00.39,Default,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,I’m glad the Substitute \NSoul Reaper after
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.39,0:02:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ginjo was a man like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.97,0:02:05.31,Default,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,That’s right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.31,0:02:08.78,Default,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,He hasn’t changed since \Nthe very beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.57,0:02:11.82,Default,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,The one man’s unchanging will
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.82,0:02:13.19,Default,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,is what changed
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.19,0:02:17.96,Default,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,the Soul Society’s \Nmillion years of rigidity.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.96,0:02:19.78,Default,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.28,0:03:00.61,Default,GINJO (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.29,0:03:08.50,Default,GINJO (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I plan to crush the Soul \NReapers who betrayed me. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.33,0:03:13.83,Default,GINJO (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And I expected you to argue \Nthat that was wrong. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.87,0:03:17.45,Default,GINJO (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Aren’t you even going to do that? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.39,0:03:19.72,Default,GINJO (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why won’t you? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.26,0:03:21.46,Default,GINJO (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The look in your eyes {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.46,0:03:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}is that of someone trying \Nto understand me…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.85,0:03:26.63,Default,GINJO (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Of someone trying to put himself in {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.63,0:03:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}my place and see things \Nfrom my perspective.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.63,0:03:30.85,Default,GINJO (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Are you telling me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.85,0:03:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}that you plan to understand me, {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.15,0:03:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and still reject everything that I am…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.73,0:03:38.36,Default,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.47,0:04:46.05,Default,GINJO (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ichigo… {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.88,0:04:49.36,Default,GINJO (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Would our roles switch {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.13,0:04:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}if you were the one who \Nhad appeared first?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.87,0:05:00.31,Default,GINJO (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Would you have become like me? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.93,0:05:03.42,Default,GINJO (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Would we, Ichigo?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.56,0:05:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If you had come first…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.73,0:05:12.25,Default,GINJO (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}would we have been… {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.73,0:05:27.80,Default,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.97,0:05:49.16,Default,TSUKISHIMA,0000,0000,0000,,Riruka…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.76,0:05:51.51,Default,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,Are you stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.00,0:05:56.16,Default,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,You were really going for the kill!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.49,0:05:57.62,Default,TSUKISHIMA,0000,0000,0000,,Out of my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.75,0:06:03.15,Default,TSUKISHIMA,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t die!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.15,0:06:05.18,Default,TSUKISHIMA,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t die, Ginjo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.79,0:06:07.51,Default,TSUKISHIMA,0000,0000,0000,,Ginjo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.51,0:06:09.13,Default,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,Face it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.75,0:06:14.54,Default,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,Face up to it already…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.02,0:06:18.94,Default,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,We…couldn’t save Ginjo…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.99,0:06:24.49,Default,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,Ginjo is the one who saved us…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.20,0:06:27.03,Default,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,But the one who saved Ginjo…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.85,0:06:31.49,Default,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,Is Ichigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.66,0:08:10.51,Default,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Are you all by yourself? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.04,0:08:12.99,Default,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I see. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.60,0:08:16.03,Default,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then we’re alike. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.70,0:08:18.75,Default,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come with me. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.30,0:08:22.19,Default,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}From today on, it’ll be the two of us. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.79,0:08:26.88,Default,TSUKISHIMA,0000,0000,0000,,Why, Ginjo?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.12,0:08:30.97,Default,TSUKISHIMA,0000,0000,0000,,You taught me how to use my powers…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.61,0:08:33.82,Default,TSUKISHIMA,0000,0000,0000,,You taught me how to fight….
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.12,0:08:36.57,Default,TSUKISHIMA,0000,0000,0000,,So why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.63,0:08:41.62,Default,TSUKISHIMA,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn’t you teach me \Nwhat to do when you died!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.23,0:08:57.26,Default,TSUKISHIMA,0000,0000,0000,,Shishigawara…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.66,0:09:03.18,Default,TSUKISHIMA,0000,0000,0000,,Oh…I see…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.18,0:09:05.74,Default,TSUKISHIMA,0000,0000,0000,,I get it…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.46,0:09:13.25,Default,JACKIE,0000,0000,0000,,You have a bad habit of kicking things.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.95,0:09:15.36,Default,JACKIE,0000,0000,0000,,You have no business lecturing Riruka.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.34,0:09:17.43,Default,YUKIO,0000,0000,0000,,Jackie.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.08,0:09:22.38,Default,YUKIO,0000,0000,0000,,You’re alive. That’s nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.00,0:09:24.66,Default,JACKIE,0000,0000,0000,,I may as well be dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.16,0:09:29.22,Default,YUKIO,0000,0000,0000,,Jackie, your Fullbring…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.22,0:09:30.17,Default,JACKIE,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.37,0:09:32.25,Default,YUKIO,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.84,0:09:34.33,Default,YUKIO,0000,0000,0000,,That’s good, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.89,0:09:36.71,Default,YUKIO,0000,0000,0000,,You were the only one
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.71,0:09:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,among us who truly \Ndetested her abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.47,0:09:41.61,Default,JACKIE,0000,0000,0000,,On my way here, I found Giriko’s
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.61,0:09:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,watch and dead body, so \NI buried them together.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.23,0:09:48.86,Default,JACKIE,0000,0000,0000,,I detested my abilities so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.86,0:09:51.31,Default,JACKIE,0000,0000,0000,,But now that I’ve lost them,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.31,0:09:56.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I kind of envy Giriko for being \Nable to die with his powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.26,0:10:01.00,Default,JACKIE,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it’s because \Nsomewhere along the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.00,0:10:07.25,Default,JACKIE,0000,0000,0000,,I realized that our Fullbrings were \Nall that connected us together…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.03,0:10:12.77,Default,YUKIO,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.74,0:10:15.05,Default,YUKIO,0000,0000,0000,,I’m leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.43,0:10:24.44,Default,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.44,0:10:26.60,Default,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you’ve come to.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.05,0:10:29.45,Default,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,I’m…alive…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.45,0:10:30.67,Default,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.67,0:10:33.41,Default,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Urahara came right after it happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.12,0:10:35.08,Default,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.98,0:10:39.98,Default,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Except for you, we couldn’t \Nfind anyone else…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.27,0:10:44.05,Default,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.80,0:10:50.07,Default,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness…Riruka…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.07,0:10:51.08,Default,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,You…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.75,0:10:55.09,Default,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,When I heard they didn’t \Nfind anyone, I…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.24,0:11:00.49,Default,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.69,0:11:13.20,Default,SHISHIGAWARA,0000,0000,0000,,After giving it a lot of \Nthought, I couldn’t…!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.89,0:11:17.64,Default,SHISHIGAWARA,0000,0000,0000,,In my mind, Mr. Tsukishima, \Nyou’re the strongest!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.78,0:11:21.02,Default,SHISHIGAWARA,0000,0000,0000,,You mustn’t die, Mr. Tsukishima!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.79,0:11:24.09,Default,SHISHIGAWARA,0000,0000,0000,,You’re the strongest, Mr. Tsukishima!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.60,0:11:25.95,Default,SHISHIGAWARA,0000,0000,0000,,You can’t die!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.34,0:11:29.63,Default,SHISHIGAWARA,0000,0000,0000,,You’re invincible, Mr. Tsukishima!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.04,0:11:36.18,Default,TSUKISHIMA (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I see now, Ginjo… {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.36,0:11:42.48,Default,TSUKISHIMA (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I’m able to finally understand \Nnow that you’re gone. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.92,0:11:47.91,Default,TSUKISHIMA (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Maybe you already knew. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.95,0:11:54.64,Default,TSUKISHIMA (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Thank you…Shishigawara. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.08,0:11:57.29,Default,SHISHIGAWARA,0000,0000,0000,,Wha-?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.29,0:11:58.86,Default,SHISHIGAWARA,0000,0000,0000,,What’re you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.25,0:12:02.40,Default,SHISHIGAWARA,0000,0000,0000,,It’s only right that I \Nhelp you, Mr. Tsukishima!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.00,0:12:06.82,Default,SHISHIGAWARA,0000,0000,0000,,After all, I am your apprentice!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.88,0:12:08.84,Default,SHISHIGAWARA,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.84,0:12:11.45,Default,SHISHIGAWARA,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Tsukishima, it’s morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.86,0:12:14.29,Default,SHISHIGAWARA,0000,0000,0000,,What a beautiful morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.29,0:12:15.87,Default,TSUKISHIMA (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}-Thank you. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.29,0:12:16.83,Default,SHISHIGAWARA,0000,0000,0000,,It’s a sight for sore eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.27,0:12:20.73,Default,TSUKISHIMA (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wasn’t alone. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.43,0:12:29.37,Default,SENTARO,0000,0000,0000,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.37,0:12:30.93,Default,KIYONE,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Ukitake!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.99,0:12:36.86,Default,SENTARO,0000,0000,0000,,Reporting, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.86,0:12:38.43,Default,SENTARO,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo Kurosaki
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.43,0:12:41.32,Default,SENTARO,0000,0000,0000,,has successfully defeated Kugo \NGinjo in the World of the Living!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.75,0:12:43.61,Default,KIYONE,0000,0000,0000,,The captains dispatched to
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.61,0:12:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,observe the battle have \Nalso safely returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.76,0:12:50.03,Default,KIYONE,0000,0000,0000,,Retrieval of Kugo Ginjo’s \Nbody is complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.42,0:12:55.47,Default,UKITAKE,0000,0000,0000,,I see…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.20,0:12:59.46,Default,KIYONE,0000,0000,0000,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.05,0:13:01.65,Default,UKITAKE,0000,0000,0000,,I’m all right…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.65,0:13:03.32,Default,UKITAKE,0000,0000,0000,,What about Ichigo?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.68,0:13:06.76,Default,SENTARO,0000,0000,0000,,Sir, Ichigo Kurosaki is safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.96,0:13:12.73,Default,UKITAKE,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.76,0:13:19.06,Default,URAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,Riruka, time for breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.03,0:13:25.65,Default,URAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,It’s got Tessai’s special pickles \Nthat he makes only for guests.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.54,0:13:29.83,Default,URAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,Riruka?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.50,0:13:31.78,Default,URAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,I’m coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.96,0:13:50.16,Default,RIRUKA (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Thank you, Ginjo, {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.10,0:13:54.31,Default,RIRUKA (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}for inviting me to join Xcution. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.45,0:13:57.95,Default,RIRUKA (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Thank you, Chad, {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.41,0:14:01.03,Default,RIRUKA (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}for believing us. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.71,0:14:09.41,Default,RIRUKA (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Thank you, Orihime, for \Ncrying tears for me. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.39,0:14:12.79,Default,RIRUKA (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And Ichigo… {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.44,0:14:17.62,Default,RIRUKA (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can say this with peace of mind… {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.11,0:14:20.28,Default,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.28,0:14:23.84,Default,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,Forget me, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.01,0:14:29.80,Default,RIRUKA (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because I know that regardless \Nof how I say goodbye,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.37,0:14:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\u1}I know you’ll never ever, {\u0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.05,0:14:39.97,Default,RIRUKA (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}forget us. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.71,0:14:51.03,Default,STEALTH FORCE,0000,0000,0000,,Reporting, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.88,0:14:54.18,Default,STEALTH FORCE,0000,0000,0000,,Lieutenant Kuchiki of \NSquad 13, who had been
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.18,0:14:56.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,clearing up affairs in \Nthe World of the Living,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.36,0:14:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,has just returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.52,0:15:02.50,Default,GENRYUSAI,0000,0000,0000,,Why’re you reporting that to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.68,0:15:04.69,Default,STEALTH FORCE,0000,0000,0000,,Sir…because…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.17,0:15:07.17,Default,BYAKUYA,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.49,0:15:11.30,Default,KENPACHI,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.30,0:15:12.29,Default,STEALTH FORCE,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.00,0:15:14.76,Default,SOI FON,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo Kurosaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.84,0:15:16.97,Default,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.83,0:15:20.44,Default,HIRAKO,0000,0000,0000,,What’d he come here \Nfor all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.08,0:15:25.12,Default,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.12,0:15:26.10,Default,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Renji!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.10,0:15:27.29,Default,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,How’re you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.29,0:15:28.53,Default,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Good…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.17,0:15:32.11,Default,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.11,0:15:34.12,Default,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,What brings you here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.12,0:15:36.13,Default,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you know…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.82,0:15:37.85,Default,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Rukia!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.85,0:15:39.81,Default,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,What’s going on? Why is he…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.81,0:15:41.47,Default,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,He says he wants to speak
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.47,0:15:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,directly with Head Captain Yamamoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.25,0:15:44.25,Default,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.60,0:15:46.76,Default,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,He just received permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.91,0:15:53.74,Default,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, just a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.26,0:15:58.31,Default,NANAO,0000,0000,0000,,What could it be about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.80,0:16:04.74,Default,SHUNSUI,0000,0000,0000,,As a fellow Substitute Soul Reaper,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.74,0:16:07.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he must have a lot on his mind…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.12,0:16:13.03,Default,SHUNSUI,0000,0000,0000,,It wouldn’t be the least bit \Nstrange if he were furious with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.30,0:16:16.99,Default,NANAO,0000,0000,0000,,Do you mean he came to \Nreturn his Combat Pass?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.52,0:16:20.74,Default,SHUNSUI,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that I couldn’t say…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.67,0:16:25.71,Default,SHUNSUI,0000,0000,0000,,It’s a sticky situation, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.10,0:16:36.42,Default,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,What’s this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.42,0:16:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you guys all here to greet me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.52,0:16:41.17,Default,SOI FON,0000,0000,0000,,Not everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.17,0:16:43.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurotsuchi and Ukitake aren’t here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.48,0:16:47.33,Default,KENSEI,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, come inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.33,0:16:48.89,Default,KENSEI,0000,0000,0000,,The Old Man is waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.89,0:16:49.73,Default,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Kensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.27,0:16:52.17,Default,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,You’re a captain now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.17,0:16:55.24,Default,KENSEI,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! I said go on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.24,0:16:57.74,Default,KENSEI,0000,0000,0000,,I’m sure you didn’t \Ncome here to chitchat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.54,0:17:06.11,Default,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Rukia, I think we should…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.11,0:17:10.69,Default,GENRYUSAI,0000,0000,0000,,Lieutenants Abarai and Kuchiki, \Nhave a seat at the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.69,0:17:11.38,Default,RENJI/RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.51,0:17:28.19,Default,GENRYUSAI,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo Kurosaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.19,0:17:30.98,Default,GENRYUSAI,0000,0000,0000,,You fought admirably.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.21,0:17:33.38,Default,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, let’s forget about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.80,0:17:36.20,Default,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,I didn’t come here today \Nto be praised for my efforts.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.94,0:17:39.16,Default,GENRYUSAI,0000,0000,0000,,Then what did you come for?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.16,0:17:40.24,Default,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.92,0:17:44.14,Default,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,It’s about Ginjo’s body, \Nthat you had Renji retrieve—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.14,0:17:47.12,Default,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,I want to bring it back to the World of \Nthe Living and give it a proper burial.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.44,0:17:50.54,Default,RUKIA (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ichigo…? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.67,0:17:53.55,Default,HIRAKO,0000,0000,0000,,Are you crazy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.80,0:17:58.01,Default,HIRAKO,0000,0000,0000,,Do you realize what you’re asking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.24,0:17:59.20,Default,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Hirako!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.85,0:18:00.68,Default,SOI FON,0000,0000,0000,,He’s right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.54,0:18:04.68,Default,SOI FON,0000,0000,0000,,The man is a heinous villain who \Nstole the powers of many Soul Reapers
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.68,0:18:06.10,Default,SOI FON,0000,0000,0000,,and murdered them one after another!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.10,0:18:06.85,Default,SOI FON,0000,0000,0000,,How could you…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.29,0:18:09.27,Default,HIRAKO,0000,0000,0000,,That’s not what I meant!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.50,0:18:11.77,Default,HIRAKO,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Ichigo…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.47,0:18:15.81,Default,HIRAKO,0000,0000,0000,,The guy messed up your \Nfamily and your friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.54,0:18:19.54,Default,HIRAKO,0000,0000,0000,,Can you forgive a guy like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.38,0:18:23.66,Default,HIRAKO,0000,0000,0000,,Or rather…should you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.54,0:18:25.49,Default,RUKIA (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ichigo… {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.08,0:18:30.69,Default,RUKIA (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Asking to bury Ginjo is synonymous \Nwith asking for his pardon… {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.69,0:18:31.61,Default,RUKIA (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That’s… {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.16,0:18:34.00,Default,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,It’s not about forgiveness.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.00,0:18:37.43,Default,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,My family and friends are \Nback to the way they were.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.80,0:18:39.22,Default,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,I’m still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.17,0:18:41.57,Default,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,And he’s…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.46,0:18:44.34,Default,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Just a Substitute Soul Reaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.21,0:18:48.00,Default,GENRYUSAI,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo Kurosaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.00,0:18:52.05,Default,GENRYUSAI,0000,0000,0000,,Can I assume you’ve \Nsaid those words after
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.05,0:18:54.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,considering all the ramifications?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.57,0:18:56.45,Default,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Screw the ramifications!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.10,0:19:01.28,Default,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,I simply want to do that for him as \Na fellow Substitute Soul Reaper…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.53,0:19:07.16,Default,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Since I am going to continue to be one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.60,0:19:08.66,Default,GENRYUSAI,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.81,0:19:15.13,Default,HIRAKO,0000,0000,0000,,So that’s it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.55,0:19:24.72,Default,GENRYUSAI,0000,0000,0000,,I will grant your request.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.15,0:19:31.62,Default,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, then I’ll be going.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.28,0:19:34.65,Default,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, by the way…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.75,0:19:39.32,Default,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,From now on, when a Soul Reaper \Ncomes to Karakura Town,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.32,0:19:42.98,Default,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,at least let them know that \Nthis is a Combat Pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.35,0:19:56.40,Default,SHUNSUI,0000,0000,0000,,I knew I’d find you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.40,0:19:57.34,Default,UKITAKE,0000,0000,0000,,Kyoraku.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.23,0:20:03.05,Default,SHUNSUI,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like Ichigo’s going back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.25,0:20:05.22,Default,UKITAKE,0000,0000,0000,,What about the Combat Pass…?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.44,0:20:08.24,Default,SHUNSUI,0000,0000,0000,,He says he’s taking it with him…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.51,0:20:11.31,Default,SHUNSUI,0000,0000,0000,,Just to be sure, I asked him…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.31,0:20:14.44,Default,SHUNSUI,0000,0000,0000,,He says he trusts us, so \Nhe’ll hold on to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.31,0:20:18.55,Default,UKITAKE,0000,0000,0000,,Oh…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.64,0:20:21.03,Default,UKITAKE,0000,0000,0000,,I see…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.25,0:20:25.97,Default,SHUNSUI,0000,0000,0000,,He’s matured, hasn’t he?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.97,0:20:26.91,Default,UKITAKE,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.79,0:20:31.53,Default,UKITAKE,0000,0000,0000,,We just didn’t realize that…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.39,0:20:37.09,Default,SHUNSUI,0000,0000,0000,,We couldn’t help it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.85,0:20:40.03,Default,SHUNSUI,0000,0000,0000,,When youngsters grow up,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.03,0:20:43.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it happens so fast that we older people
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.55,0:20:45.67,Default,SHUNSUI,0000,0000,0000,,never see it coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.52,0:21:13.66,Default,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.84,0:21:16.21,Default,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,See you around, Rukia.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.21,0:21:25.72,Default,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how many times \NI’ve heard you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.36,0:21:28.85,Default,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,This isn’t going to be the last time,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.85,0:21:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so who cares how many times I say it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.93,0:21:34.19,Default,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,You’re right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.01,0:23:24.67,Default,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,Kurosaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.67,0:23:26.40,Default,ISHIDA,0000,0000,0000,,What took you, Kurosaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.30,0:23:30.37,Default,YUZU,0000,0000,0000,,Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.37,0:23:31.94,Default,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,Yuzu, Brother Ichi is over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.94,0:23:34.14,Default,KEIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.14,0:23:35.31,Default,MIZUIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.92,0:23:49.83,OS,CAPTION,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1600,1)}ICHIGO KUROSAKI / 17 YEARS OLD \NHAIR COLOR / ORANGE \NEYE COLOR / BROWN \NOCCUPATION / HIGH SCHOOL STUDENT \N& SUBSTITUTE SOUL REAPER
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.27,0:23:47.71,Default,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,See you again…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.24,0:23:51.24,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,